taxes and other governmental and quasi-governmental fees.<strong>EXCEPT AND UNLESS SPECIFICALLY PROHIBITED BY LAW, SUCH CREDIT SHALL BE YOUR SOLE AND EXCLUSIVE REMEDY FOR AN INTERRUPTION OF SERVICE(S).</strong> Any credits provided by Comcast are at our sole discretion and in no event shall constitute or be construed as a course of conduct by Comcast. </p>
