 of any changes and the effective date. If you find the change unacceptable, you  have the right to cancel your service. However, if you continue to receive our service after the effective date of the change, we will consider this your acceptance of the change.  <BR><BR>For those of our customers receiving service through commercial accounts, bulk rate arrangements or similar arrangements, some of the policies, procedures and  services herein may not apply. Please call us at the local customer service number listed on the How to Reach Us insert to talk to one of our customer service representatives for  further information.</P>--></p>
